data.description: This Gulf Gate gem shows beautifully and is immaculate inside and out..spacious, light, bright and airy inside with a private fenced yard and just a mere 3 miles to our world-famous sugar sand beach of Siesta Key FL !    Start off with the beautiful curb appeal.. lush landscaping, fresh paint and beautiful new glass-paned double doors which allow for streams of natural sunlight to enter the home.  Easy care wood plank ceramic tile will be found throughout all of the living areas in this home along with all of the bedrooms. The gourmet kitchen overlooks the bonus sunroom and is SO nice ...you can feel and see the quality choices and workmanship which include thick slabs of granite on the counters and backsplash, gleaming stainless steel appliances (convection oven and french door style frig)  Generously sized bedrooms, a smart split floor plan, large bay window, walk in closets, plantation shutters, crown molding and gorgeous modern colors. This home was also re-piped with PVC, the roof was replaced in 2013, AC replaced in 2016 with a higher quality unit, new Rheem hot water heater in 2018.  Location cannot be beat.. minutes to shopping, dining, downtown Sarasota, movie theaters, Costco and so much more.  Walk to Gulf Gate Elementary (which is also a shelter)   this home is also zoned for Riverview HS !
